The '''Atlanta Trumpet Festival''' is hosted by the Atlanta Trumpet Ensemble under the direction of Kay and David Fairchild.<ref name =Kay/><ref name=David/> The [[Music festival|festival]] started in conjunction with the creation of the "[[Atlanta]] Youth Trumpet Ensemble" in 2004 which has since been renamed the Atlanta Trumpet Ensemble. The festival occurs annually around mid-September and lasts a total of two days. Throughout the day [[trumpet]] players from around [[North America]] participate in [[Rehearsal|rehearsals]] and clinics given by some of the finest trumpet instructors of the [[United States]].<ref>[http://atlantatrumpetfestival.com/artists.htm Artists and Conductors] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928120234/http://atlantatrumpetfestival.com/artists.htm |date=September 28, 2007 }}</ref>
